I am just saying, why are we penalized for something we dont' have any control over.  I think all pet classes would agree with that.<br>
<br>
Why did they fix the No Rent issue?  I am sure it was because so many people complained about no rent items going POOF from stupid LD issues... no one was using the Summoned Bags because all their stuff would be lost if they went LD.  Quests involving no rent items were extremely hard, if not impossible to do for some people that go LD with nearly every time they zone.<br>
<br>
